ndustrial courtyard. The man in the yellow jacket stands beside the front of the truck with one arm resting on the hood or fender, facing forward. The silver pickup sits angled behind him, its extended cab and open bed visible, with wet-looking pavement and the old building surrounding it. He remains in place as the truck is presented one last time.",
